HEADWORD: Furthersome
<hw>Fur"ther*some</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Tending to
further, advance, or promote; helpful; advantageous.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

